description: This is a market on whether Chelsea will qualify for the 2021-2022 UEFA Champions League, by the resolution date, May 29, 11:59 PM ET. This market will resolve to “Yes” if the Chelsea Football Club qualifies to compete in the 2021–22 UEFA Champions League by the resolution date. Otherwise, this market will resolve to “No.” If the 2020-2021 Champions League final or Premier League fixtures are delayed for any reason, resolution of this market will be delayed until the final results of both the 2020-2021 Premier League and Champions League are available. If results are unavailable for either competition by August 1, 2021, this market will resolve to 50-50. In the event of ambiguity in terms of the market outcome, this market will be resolved in good faith at the sole discretion of the Markets Integrity Committee (MIC).
